  "keyFeatures": [
    "Base classes for VST 3 audio effect and controller implementation (AudioEffect, EditController, SingleComponentEffect)",
    "Cross-platform plug-in module loader for VST 3 hosts (VST3::Hosting::Module)",
    "AAX, AU, and AUv3 format wrappers to wrap VST 3 plug-ins for ProTools and macOS/iOS",
    "Parameter management system with RangeParameter, StringListParameter, and ParameterContainer",
    "Rich set of hosting helper classes: PluginFactory, PluginProvider, EventList, ParameterChanges",
    "20+ sample VST 3 plug-ins demonstrating gain, delay, synthesis, panning, MIDI, and more",
    "Sample host applications: AudioHost, EditorHost, InspectorApp, and Validator",
    "Utility classes: MPE processor, data exchange, ring buffer, sample-accurate parameters"
  ],
